thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by ngrodgers1

author: ngrodgers1
title: ngrodgers1
text: As an avid fisherman I was very skeptical on signing up for something like this . But the field of work im in makes it hard to get to any of the pro shops to purchase tackle . After receiving the first couple months boxes I knew I was gonna be hooked for life. The quantity and quality that is put into each box is amazing and it really does work . Just used a couple of the jerk baits while river fishing in mid February and absolutely nailed smallmouth . I highly recommend this company
